Interface ConfigurationEntryDispatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultConfigurationFileChangeListener

    public interface ConfigurationEntryDispatcher
    Dispatches configuration entries to registered configuration handlers.

    • Method Detail

      • addHandler

        void addHandler(Set<ConfigurationLineClassifier> classifiers,
              ConfigurationEntryHandler handler)
        Adds a handler as observer for configuration lines with the given configuration line classifiers. Configuration line classifiers, that are not supported by the dispatcher are ignored.
        Parameters:
        classifiers - the configuration line classifiers
        handler - the handler to add

      • removeHandler

        void removeHandler(Set<ConfigurationLineClassifier> classifiers,
                 ConfigurationEntryHandler handler)
        Removes a handler as observer for configuration lines with the given configuration line classifiers. Configuration line classifiers, that are not supported by the dispatcher are ignored.
        Parameters:
        classifiers - the configuration line classifiers
        handler - the handler to remove
